      "atAGlance": "<ul><li><b>Input:</b> [[trigeminal_nerve]] (via trigeminothalamic tract) and Gustatory pathway.</li><li><b>Output:</b> Primary [[somatosensory_cortex]].</li><li><b>Information Type:</b> Somatosensory input from the <b>Face</b> and <b>Taste</b>.</li><li><b>USMLE Tip:</b> Mnemonic: V<b>P</b>M = <b>M</b>akeup goes on the <b>Face</b> (or <b>M</b>outh for taste).</li></ul>",
