      "takeAway": "<p>The <b>Area Postrema</b> is the medullary chemoreceptor trigger zone that monitors blood for toxins due to its absent [[blood_brain_barrier]], initiating the vomiting reflex via D2 and 5-HT3 receptors.</p>",
