      "definition": "<p><b>Cranial Nerve Vascular Relationships</b> describe the specific anatomical proximities between cranial nerves and cerebral arteries, which are critical for localizing [[aneurysm]]s or vascular compressions that result in specific nerve palsies.</p>",
