      "takeAway": "<p>Understanding the four <b>Dopaminergic Pathways</b> explains the therapeutic effects (Mesolimbic blockade) and side effects (Nigrostriatal EPS, Tuberoinfundibular hyperprolactinemia) of antipsychotics.</p>",
