      "definition": "<p><b>Hypothalamic Appetite Regulation</b> involves the interplay between the <u>Lateral Hypothalamus</u> (Hunger center) and the <u>Ventromedial Hypothalamus</u> (Satiety center), regulated by hormones like Ghrelin and Leptin.</p>",
